    "title": "Labs concoct spells",
    "body": "Hover your Lab and click Concoct → Freeze. After ~15 seconds the spell is ready.\n\nTo cast: drag from your ready Lab to any node. Freeze instantly neutralizes the target — units preserved, ownership erased.\n\nLabs cannot produce units, only consume them. The red main base is too strong to take by force. Freeze it, then capture the empty shell."
